🔥 🔹 Access Review kya hai?
👉 Access Review (Certification) ka matlab:-
User ke paas jo access (roles, entitlements) hai wo sahi hai ya nahi — ye check karna
Jab tu AccessReview object create ya update karta hai, wo DB me persist hota hai.

🧠 Simple Example:-
User: Rahul
Access:
- Admin Role ❌ (shayad zarurat nahi)
- Read Access ✅

👉 Manager bole:-
Admin remove karo ❌
Read rehne do ✅
👉 Ye hi Access Review hai

🔥 🔹 Ye kya karta hai?
👉 System automatically:-
Users ka access list nikalta hai
Reviewer (Manager / Admin) ko bhejta hai
Wo decide karta hai:-
Approve ✅
Revoke ❌
Phir system action leta hai.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
🔥 🔹 Access Review ke andar kya hota hai?
1. 🔹 Identity (User):-
👉 Jiska access review ho raha hai

2. 🔹 Reviewer:-
👉 Kaun check karega (Manager / App Owner)

3. 🔹 Items:-
👉 Kya review ho raha hai:-
Roles
Entitlements
Accounts

4. 🔹 Decision:-
👉 Reviewer kya karega:-
Approve
Revoke
Delegate

5. 🔹 Comments:-
👉 Kyun approve/reject kiya

6. 🔹 Due Date:-
👉 Kab tak review complete karna hai

7. 🔹 Status:-
👉 Current state:-
Open
Completed
Expired
---------------------------------------------------------------------
🔥 🔹 Real Flow (Step by Step):-
1. Campaign create hota hai
2. Users select hote hain
3. Reviewer assign hota hai
4. Access list show hoti hai
5. Reviewer decision deta hai
6. System revoke / keep karta hai.
-----------------------------------------------------
🔥 🔹 Types of Access Review:-
1. 🔹 Manager Review:-
👉 Manager apne team ka access check karta hai.

2. 🔹 Application Owner Review:-
👉 App owner apne system ka access check karta hai.

3. 🔹 Role Review:-
👉 Roles verify hote hain.

4. 🔹 Entitlement Review:-
👉 Permissions check hoti hain.
-----------------------------------------------------------
()Status in AccessReview:-
🔹 1. OPEN / ACTIVE:-
Matlab: review ya policy abhi pending hai
Reviewer ne abhi action nahi liya
System wait kar raha hai response ka
Example:-
Campaign: Quarterly Access Review
Status: OPEN
👉 Action: Reviewer ko notify karega

🔹 2. COMPLETED / CLOSED:-
Matlab: review complete ho gaya
Sab approvals/rejections submit ho gaye
System koi further action nahi lega
Example:-
Status: COMPLETED
Decision: 5 approved, 2 revoked

🔹 3. EXPIRED:-
Matlab: review ka due date pass ho gaya
Reviewer ne decision nahi liya
System automatic escalation ya default action le sakta hai
Example:-
Status: EXPIRED
Action: Notify Manager / Auto Revoke

🔹 4. IN_PROGRESS:-
Matlab: review process chal raha hai
Reviewer kuch decisions le chuka hai, baki pending hai

🔹 5. SUSPENDED / LOCKED:-
Matlab: review temporarily stop hai
Ho sakta hai policy ya system reason se hold pe hai

🔹 6. CANCELLED:-
Matlab: review ya policy ko cancel kar diya gaya
Koi action nahi hoga.
